    "data": [
        [
            [
                "Dialogue"
            ],
            [
                "What? No! I work at the coffee shop where the hell would I get any money from"
            ],
            [
                "I take a deep breath before.."
            ],
            [
                "Hmmm..... HEEEYY! HEEL-"
            ],
            [
                "SHHH HEY! HEY NO NO! NO! SHUT IT! SHUSH, SHUSH NOW!"
            ],
            [
                "DAMMIT, FINE. WHAT ABOUT COFFEE, I'LL GIVE YOU A FREE COFFEE. ON THE HOUSE AND ALL. PLEASE! SHUSH! NOW!"
            ],
            [
                "The offer is now a positive for me."
            ],
            [
                "you promise?"
            ],
            [
                "Hell yeah I promise."
            ],
            [
                "The manager comes near my table, and eerie presence combined with her face rock solid with an expression of pure unfilitered tension."
            ],
            [
                "She comes near, but I keep myself silent. A part of me is also afraid. Her stare is enough to cut the air as a sharp sword."
            ],
            [
                "...................."
            ],
            [
                "She leaves and I feel the aura of terror light up. Victor wasn't whining, she really is scary. Exchanging words with her would absolutely make me cry."
            ],
            [
                "Is... is she gone."
            ],
            [
                "I... I think so, yeah."
            ],
            [
                "Pheww."
            ],
            [
                "I swear my heart almost pops out. Geez"
            ],
            [
                "Yeah... mine too. Are you sure that thing is human?"
            ],
            [
                "Well, I can at least say that she's got the tiniest heart if any."
            ],
            [
                "She's the kind of people, folklore borns myths out of to scare children."
            ],
            [
                "It did scare me at my rip old age."
            ],
            [
                "Well, yeah. wild shift huh? But... thanks for helping me out."
            ],
            [
                "What help? You owe me now."
            ],
            [
                "A coffee? Alright, sure. It will be all yours, just... not right now. I might hide in the freezer for some time. "
            ],
            [
                "But you can come for your prize tomorrow. I'll be waiting for you. Hey, free coffee any day any time, as long as you help me out."
            ],
            [
                "You will really give me free coffee? Do you promise?"
            ],
            [
                "Absolutely, yeah!"
            ],
            [
                "Victor looks both ways before curving into the employees only room."
            ],
            [
                "Hey free coffee! I guess."
            ]
